{"Id":867303,"Title":"行香子三首  三十初度自寿","Dynasty":"近现代","Author":"顾随","Context":"陆起龙蛇。归去无家。又东风、悄换年华。已甘沦落。莫漫嗟呀。拚一枝烟，一壶酒，一杯茶。我似乘槎，西渡流沙。走红尘、晚日朝霞。卅年岁月，廿载天涯。共愁中乐，苦中笑，梦中花。不作超人。莫怕沈沦。一杯杯、酸酒沾唇。读书自苦，卖赋犹贫。又者般疯，者般傻，者般浑。莫漫殷勤，徒事纷纭。浪年华、断送閒身。倚阑强笑。回首酸辛。算十年风，十年雨，十年尘。春日迟迟。怅怅何之。鬓星星、八字微髭。近来生活，力尽声嘶。问几人怜，几人恨，几人知。少岁吟诗，中岁填词。把牢骚、徒做谈资。镇常自语，待得何时。可唤愁来，鞭愁死，葬愁尸。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"行香子","Status":2,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"d47f71b4bc083ad0ebcbb958ff2a1c9a","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":5089091,"Sentence":"回首酸辛。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"huǐ shǒu suān xīn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":18,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5089073,"Sentence":"陆起龙蛇。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"lìu qi lóng shé ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5089074,"Sentence":"归去无家。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"guī qù mó gū ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5089076,"Sentence":"已甘沦落。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yi gān lún là ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5089077,"Sentence":"莫漫嗟呀。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"mò màn jiē yā ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5089083,"Sentence":"不作超人。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"bú zuō chāo rén ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":10,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5089084,"Sentence":"莫怕沈沦。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"mò pà shěn lún ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":11,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5089090,"Sentence":"倚阑强笑。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yi lán jiàng xiào ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":17,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5089075,"Sentence":"又东风、悄换年华。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yòu dōng fēng 、qiāo huàn nián huā ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5089079,"Sentence":"我似乘槎，西渡流沙。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wǒ s